{"tid":421574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寒 十一月 遊人望鄉心切","createTime":"2017-10-02T10:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T10:43:18.000Z","uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17a949bb7c6b489b176440061fbc29d54750ac55","tid":421574,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uf2lun7Ah-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fuf2lun7Ah-0&d=dbPDPaYoj6NyKd01Z6DEHgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=50cb9dca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uf2lun7Ah-0</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每一次聽都會諗返起唔同既往事 <br />\n雖然好多歌都有咁既效果<br />\n但係呢首歌既曲 詞同e臣既震音 <br />\n真係夾得好完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一唱寒果下真係雞皮都起鳩埋 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後果一句 前 路不斷 在雪下前 淚要落完 <br />\n聽完之後你既思緒真係跟住首歌既音樂一齊停止 <br />\n所有既往事都唔再重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似浮雲一樣 <br />\n著重既 只係呢一刻既安寧"}]}